name: Ill-fated
description: 'This godforsaken cloud keeps following me everywhere I go. I've tried making peace with it by offering it a piece of my soul but it just won't budge no matter what from it's motive which is to follow me around day and night. Every time I look up, I see the dratted cloud hover threateningly over my self. Now that all my reconciliation attempts have proved to be futile, I'm beginning to suspect the said cloud has vile intentions towards me and all of humanity as such.  Oh no it's keep getting bigger as I write this down as my plea for help. OH NO, I don't ha-'
